long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
"Getting Over It - Unblocked Games" is a challenging and frustratingly addictive physics-based platformer available as a Chrome extension. In this unique game, you control a character named Diogenes, who is stuck in a cauldron and must climb a treacherous mountain using only a hammer. Maneuvering through the obstacles requires precise movements and careful planning to avoid falling back to the beginning. With its minimalist graphics, atmospheric soundtrack, and steep difficulty curve, "Getting Over It" tests your patience, determination, and resilience. The Chrome extension provides easy access, allowing you to play the game directly in your browser. Prepare to embrace the frustration and embark on a journey of perseverance and triumph in "Getting Over It - Unblocked Games"!

If you want play more games please click on "Unblocked Games, Web Version" and click on web version for play on our website  https://unblockedgames.ee/
